OL,5,Cfreed
OL,7,FA 'sadistic' killer who stabbed his
OL,8,Fvictim 60 times on Christmas Day 1997
OL,9,Fis to be freed from prison after a
OL,10,Fjudge refused an application to
OL,11,Freconsider the Parole Board's
OL,12,Frecommendation for his release.
OL,14,FSteven Ling was jailed for life after
OL,15,Fadmitting to the murder of 29-year-old
OL,16,FJoanne Tulip in Stamfordham,
OL,17,FNorthumberland. He told police he had
OL,18,Fraped Joanne.
