OL,7,FHowever, on Tuesday (22 October) the
OL,8,FParole Board confirmed this
OL,9,Fapplication had been rejected and
OL,10,Fkiller would be released.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the Parole Board
OL,13,Fsaid: "An application for
OL,14,Freconsideration was made by the
OL,15,FSecretary of State for Justice in the
OL,16,Fcase of Steven Ling on 30 September
OL,17,F2024.
