OL,4,C60 times on Christmas Day 1997 to be
OL,5,Cfreed
OL,7,F"That application challenged the
OL,8,FParole Board's decision to direct his
OL,9,Frelease following a public hearing in
OL,10,FJuly 2024.
OL,12,F"A Judge at the Parole Board
OL,13,Fconsidered the application for
OL,14,Freconsideration and has decided, based
OL,15,Fon the evidence, that it will be
OL,16,Frefused.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/10
