OL,4,C60 times on Christmas Day 1997 to be
OL,5,Cfreed
OL,7,FJoanne's mother, Doreen Soulsby,
OL,8,Fpreviously condemned the decision by
OL,9,Fthe Parole Board, and said: "This is a
OL,10,Fman who committed the most horrific
OL,11,Fsadistic crimes against my daughter,
OL,12,Fincluding stabbing her 60 times and
OL,13,Fraping her, after having consumed a
OL,14,Fsignificant amount of alcohol.
OL,16,F"Ling has spent 27 years in custody
OL,17,Fwithout having had sex. There is a
OL,18,Fpossibility that once he is let out in
OL,19,Fthe community, he will seriously harm
OL,20,Fother women and will use force to do
OL,21,Fso, as he did with Joanne.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/10
