OL,5,Cfreed
OL,7,F"There is nothing that can be done to
OL,8,Fstop this man constantly thinking he
OL,9,Fis entitled to sex."
OL,11,FLing, a farm worker, was inspired to
OL,12,Fmurder Ms Tulip on Christmas Day 1997
OL,13,Fby sadism, Newcastle Crown Court heard
OL,14,Fat the time.
OL,16,FA charge of rape was left on file
OL,17,Fduring the original court case, so he
OL,18,Fis not a convicted sex offender.
OL,19,FHowever in its ruling, the Parole
OL,20,FBoard said: "Mr Ling has always
OL,21,Faccepted that he raped the victim."
