OL,4,C60 times on Christmas Day 1997 to be
OL,5,Cfreed
OL,7,FDuring sentencing, Mr Justice Potts
OL,8,Ftold Ling, who was 23 at the time of
OL,9,Fthe murder: "You will never be
OL,10,Freleased so long as it is thought you
OL,11,Fconstitute a danger to women."
OL,13,FHe was given life with a minimum term
OL,14,Fof 20 years, which was reduced to 18
OL,15,Fyears by the High Court.
OL,17,FThe only route to further challenge
OL,18,Fthis decision is via judicial review.
